Heat oven to 350 degrees F. Mix dressing, broccoli, pimientos, Parmesan cheese and 1/2 cup mozzarella cheese. Bake 20 to 25 min. or until heated through. Spread into 1-qt. baking dish or 9-inch pie plate. Sprinkle with remaining mozzarella cheese; bake 5 min. or until cheese is melted. Serve with crackers.